title: 2048 Game
description: The website you are currently looking at.

body.raw:
### **Description:**  
Developed a web-based recreation of the classic 2048 game to deepen my understanding of web development. This project helped me learn the fundamentals of **HTML**, **CSS**, and how they interact with **JavaScript** to create dynamic, interactive functionality.

---

### **Tech Stack:**  
- **Frontend**: HTML, CSS, JavaScript  
- **Focus Areas**: Responsive design, dynamic DOM manipulation  

This project reflects my foundational skills in building interactive web applications while exploring the basics of game development.  
[GitHub Repository](https://github.com/chanbinna/2048)
